remarks.para:
Absolute and relative #get() <i>get</i> and
              #put(int) <i>put</i> methods that read and write
              single ints;

remarks.code:
{@code
                for (int i = off; i < off + len; i++)
                    dst[i] = src.get();
            }

Docs.param:
The number of ints to be read from the given array;
                    must be non-negative and no larger than
                    array.length - offset

remarks.code:
{@code
                for (int i = off; i < off + len; i++)
                    dst.put(a[i]);
            }
